## Heritage Shield Technology

Heritage Shield is our specialized line of shield-style emblems, combining traditional craftsmanship with modern technology to create collectible pieces.

### Key Features

- **Hand-applied vitrified enamel** — vibrant colors that last generations
- **Three-dimensional relief** — up to 3 depth levels
- **Precious metal finishes** — genuine gold and silver options

### Tradition and Prestige

From centuries-old universities to legendary sports clubs, Heritage Shield represents excellence in institutional emblems.
